      <title>特朗普重启对 1 月 6 日民事诉讼的豁免权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-25/trump-revives-bid-for-immunity-against-jan-6-civil-lawsuits</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统再次推动结束民事诉讼，该诉讼旨在要求他对 2021 年 1 月 6 日美国国会大厦袭击期间的暴力行为和破坏国会负责。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-25/trump-revives-bid-for-immunity-against-jan-6-civil-lawsuits</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 25 Jan 2025 03:08:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>赫格塞斯赢得参议院批准出任五角大楼职位，向特朗普低头</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-25/hegseth-on-verge-of-confirmation-with-vance-to-break-senate-tie</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管皮特·赫格塞斯缺乏高层经验，且受到酗酒、性行为不端以及他之前所领导的组织的财务管理不善等指控（他予以否认），但参议院多数党仍确认了特朗普总统的选择，皮特·赫格塞斯将成为下一任国防部长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-25/hegseth-on-verge-of-confirmation-with-vance-to-break-senate-tie</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 25 Jan 2025 02:38:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
