      <title>新西兰外交部长对加强与美国的关系充满信心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-25/new-zealand-foreign-minister-confident-of-stronger-us-relations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新西兰外交部长温斯顿·彼得斯在与美国国务卿马尔科·卢比奥通话后表示，新西兰有信心与美国的关系会越来越牢固。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-25/new-zealand-foreign-minister-confident-of-stronger-us-relations</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 25 Jan 2025 00:06:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
